This map is made to have a gravity effect similar to the earths so do not be afraid to go over the edge of the cube for you will just flip to the next side of thec ube and keep going.
the CT spawn is on top of the cube and the T spawn is on the bottom of the cube.



please do not put this map up on any websight. and dont decompile this map with out my permision.
